      • debugStartListeningForIncomingCalls

        public void debugStartListeningForIncomingCalls()
        Sets the SDK in a state where it listens for incoming phone calls without the need for receiving a push notification. You should use this for debugging/testing purposes only, using this in production will consume significant battery life.

      • debugStopListeningForIncomingCalls
